Personas:
——————————————————————————————————————————
A fictional character that represents the wants and needs of a customer. They should represent a specific target audience. 

A well-crafted buyer persona will help you understand your ideal customer and their goals, provide guidance on how to tailor your marketing strategy, guide product development, and help you prioritize your time.

What to include in a persona:
	1. Name 
	2. Demographics (age, gender, education, income)
	3. Interests/hobbies
	4. Goals and objectives
	5. Pain points

Look to use a persona template with nice visuals to make things easier
